{"tid":1720962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解呢時呢刻仲著黑衫？","createTime":"2019-11-14T13:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T14:15:26.000Z","uid":12555,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"70092e710e018f27739d9533048058ccc136b4b5","tid":1720962,"uid":12555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:50:28.000Z","msg":"你著晒黑衫俾人點晒相，啲狗都昅實你。<br />\n<br />\n如果著返白衫、用對家嘅制服，再混返入佢地度唔係仲好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家香港勇武就武啦，但好似唔識滲透咁，對家用呢招捉返勇武、和理非，點解唔用同一招？<br />\n<br />\n特登喺佢地啲group度爆料、放流料，嚇到佢地連出都唔敢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你知啲藍絲無人陪就成隻死狗咁縮埋一二邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fd8be307000b6feec0da5c7444b6b9afbf2c87","tid":1720962,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T13:53:15.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca20928f550b5999a5e83e51ad6baf6241aa652f","tid":1720962,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:09:55.000Z","msg":"黑衫係團體式做野先著，單拖唔洗，仲危險"},{"pid":"8c27c8d75cc7df495a494b1c1090ce118163d593","tid":1720962,"uid":71864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"呢排天氣轉涼出街要帶件外套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3aa893044a96a398b8bf5ee74492925da1c74c","tid":1720962,"uid":86495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"風向撚唔洗再帶風向，一啲又話冇用，一啲又話再留會毒死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720909</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}